  "version_note": "v2.0.3 (2026-07-14): comprehensive dataset+join audit \u2014 every one of the 514,696-athlete release's schools cross-checked vs the official NCAA directory and individually web-verified for the 2025-26 season (2 workflows, ~137 agents, adversarial refutation). Removed out-of-scope non-NCAA-in-2025-26 schools: Shawnee State (NAIA, 172) and Johnson & Wales University Charlotte (NCAA exploratory/USCAA, 217). Kept 6 NCAA provisional members (Jamestown, Roosevelt, Point Park, Carlow, Regent, Middle Georgia State). Web-verified 2025-26 conference corrections: Notre Dame (per-sport ACC/Big Ten hockey/Independent football), SUNY Brockport->Empire 8, SUNY Canton->SUNYAC, Upper Iowa->GLVC, Penn College->United East, Vermont State Lyndon->North Atlantic, Salve Regina->NEWMAC, Norwich->GNAC, Utica->Empire 8, Marywood->Atlantic East. Backfilled school_state for 133 schools (~58.7k rows) from Scorecard; enriched SES for 5 schools; fixed Missouri S&T IPEDS join (config). 515,085 -> 514,696. Schema unchanged. v2.0.1 (2026-07-13): removed 308 Louisiana Christian University (NAIA) rows mis-scraped into the Louisiana/UL-Lafayette path, and corrected conference/division labels to 2025-26 vintage. 515,393 -> 515,085. Schema unchanged. v2.0 adds high-school public/private/religious classification (NCES CCD+PSS) and Census-validated town income/population (ACS 2022), replacing mis-scaled hometown_population.",
